flowchart LR
    SIGNAL["Wait returns<br/>in milliseconds"]:::signal --> WHY{"Possible explanation"}:::decision
    WHY --> CURRENT["Current condition<br/>already true"]:::valid
    WHY --> PREVIOUS["Previous lifecycle<br/>state reused"]:::risk
    CURRENT --> AMBIGUOUS["Elapsed time alone<br/>does not prove stale state"]:::neutral
    PREVIOUS --> EVIDENCE["Correlate UID, generation,<br/>resource version, or transition"]:::evidence
    EVIDENCE --> STALE["Stale-state conclusion<br/>is supported"]:::claim

    classDef signal fill:#dae8fc,stroke:#6c8ebf,color:#172554;
    classDef decision fill:#fff2cc,stroke:#d6b656,color:#713f12;
    classDef valid fill:#d5e8d4,stroke:#82b366,color:#14532d;
    classDef risk fill:#f8cecc,stroke:#b85450,color:#7f1d1d,stroke-dasharray:6 4;
    classDef evidence fill:#e1d5e7,stroke:#9673a6,color:#4c1d95;
    classDef claim fill:#d5e8d4,stroke:#82b366,color:#14532d;
    classDef neutral fill:#f5f5f5,stroke:#666666,color:#262626;
